parameters:
Mage Relm: Ah, I found it! The literature was right after
all!

Thief Nora: Is this mold? There was a time when I ate bread
that had this kind of thing growing on it!

Mage Relm: This moss is an incredibly excellent medium for
magic! The timing was perfect considering the seasonal
issue!
Mage Relm: Now, let's collect it without getting hurt--
Court Mage Eratoma: Hello, everyone! What a coincidence!

Mage Relm: I'm in the middle of work right now! Whoever you
are, please don't disturb me... Oh, it's you!?

Court Mage Eratoma: It's been a while since the dragon
subjugation party, huh? Ahaha, everyone seems to be doing
well, which is great.

Court Mage Eratoma: May I have a little bit? I really need
moss for my current research.

Mage Relm: Yes, of course. It's not like it belongs to me or
anything.

Court Mage Eratoma: Ahaha, that's right, that's how it is!
The earth, the sky, and even this place, they belong to no
one.

Court Mage Eratoma: Yes, it seems that a talented mage has
gone missing.

Court Mage Eratoma: As a talented mage like you, please take
care on your journey, then.

Thief Nora: U-Um, she's someone I'm not very good with... I
can't really tell what she's thinking... Ugh.

Mage Relm: I'm not good with her either. I don't understand
why she was chosen as the Court Mage.

Priestess Sophia: ...It seems Caron-sama chose her for the
position.

Mage Relm: I was able to peel it off skillfully! With this,
I am one step closer to my dream. Thank you very much!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I am also happy. As a celebration
for getting one step closer to my dream... *sigh*!

Mage Relm: You're always drinking, aren't you! Well, since
you're in such a good mood today, it's not a problem!

Thief Nora: Shouldn't we leave soon...? Those people from
earlier might come back!
Clea: Yes, I think it's unnecessary to stay here any longer.
